### Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7059
@contentType = application/json

### STEP 1: Register a user first (REQUIRED before creating clients!)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "malia@camandang.com",
  "password": "Test123!",
  "firstName": "Malia",
  "lastName": "Camandang",
  "phoneNumber": "222-2222"
}

###

### Get all users (copy the userId for next step)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Auth/users

###

### STEP 2: Create a client using the userId from above
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Clients
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": "638b9373-98bd-494b-b942-ebc3ce76fe92",
  "address": "Monsters Inc, Long Beach, California"
}

###

### Get all clients (NOW you'll see data!)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Clients

###

### Get client by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Clients/3

###

### Get client by User ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Clients/user/c77c4d34-7c0c-42cc-9c1d-03ed2a99b07f

###

### Create a new client
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Clients
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": "test-user-id",
  "address": "123 Main Street, City, State"
}

###

### Update a client
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/Clients/3
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": "c77c4d34-7c0c-42cc-9c1d-03ed2a99b07f",
  "address": "456 Oak Avenue, City, State"
}

###

### Delete a client
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/Clients/1

###

### Get client's vehicles
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Clients/2/vehicles

###

### Get client's service requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Clients/1/servicerequests

###
